      <title>亿万富翁 Jeff Yass 支持一家实施 DEI 政策的非营利组织</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/billionaire-yass-backed-a-nonprofit-that-took-on-dei-policies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁杰夫·亚斯的基金会花费了数十万美元支持一个非营利组织，该组织代表那些在全国学校和立法机构中反对多元化倡议、批判种族理论计划和其他热门话题的人提起诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/billionaire-yass-backed-a-nonprofit-that-took-on-dei-policies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 19:54:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
