      <title>亿万富翁贾斯汀·伊什比亚考虑竞购美国职业棒球大联盟明尼苏达双城队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/billionaire-justin-ishbia-weighs-bid-for-mlb-s-minnesota-twins</link>
